{
  "stem": "26142.16",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Among our groups, I know-- he-- he and one guy would-- would mark-- mark, like they mark the cattle in-- in Texas, I saw on CNET with-- with-- with green or red paint on the forehead.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They were-- a red one was-- was to death and a green one was to life.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But most of our people that came that day were-- were passed-- passed through-- through for life.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I know one had a hernia and one guy, he was a married guy that had a-- he had a stomach operation done because he had a big-- big cut on the stomach.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You could see it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He was taken out and we never-- we never saw him again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But here is the biggest spectacle that we encountered was Christmas Eve, 1944.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Next day, all the-- the labor units that went out to work were called in early and instead of taking them inside, into the block, where-- in-- in-- where they brought in the-- the food, whatever they-- whatever they had-- well, it was supposed to be the macaroni and-- and marmalade.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They told them to-- to line up on the appelplatz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Lined up on the appelplatz, and then we got an order to-- to get out also.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And this was like an amphitheater, like on a-- on a mountain.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So we were-- we were, more or less, at the end-- at the end of-- of the group, and there were roughly between 5,000 and 6,000 inmates over there.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We could-- we could see the-- the-- the-- the guards on the towers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They were all in the- in-- in-- in-- in the heavy pelts, clothing because it was very windy and very cold in December in Bavaria.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "It's-- it's-- we were shivering.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
